Description:
In the frozen sewers you find many ratmen corpses, as well as patrols of the frozen dead. You do your best to avoid them and not raise the alarm.

As you proceed, in a small room, you find some gold and a mysterious key that doesn't seem to belong in the sewers.

You decide that this is dangerous and look for a way out, you see the bottom of a well that connects with the city.
DescriptionAction: Near the outside of the well you see a nearby patrol, so you try to calculate the best time to get out.
